title: Cherry chocolate upside down cake
ingredients: ['600g tinned cherry fruit filling', '280g plain flour', '300g caster sugar', '65g unsweetened cocoa powder', '1 1/2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '3/4 teaspoon salt', '350ml water', '120ml vegetable oil', '60ml vinegar', '1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract']
